    {
      "card": {
        "bgColor": "var(--gray-3)",
        "label": "Lesson 12 • Running a meeting",
        "descriptions": [
          {
            "description": [
              {
                "text": "Julia is running a meeting. When Larry and Sally start arguing, Julia has to bring the meeting back under control."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Julia: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Let’s "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"get down to business"
            },
            {
              "text":	". We need to "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"cover a lot of ground"
            },
            {
              "text":	". Our first "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"agenda item"
            },
            {
              "text":	" is to figure out how we’re going to respond to all the complaints we’ve been getting about our new website."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Larry: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Just so we’re all "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"on the same page"
            },
            {
              "text":	", please give us an overview of the problem."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Julia: "
            },
            {
              "markedText": "In a nutshell"
            },
            {
              "text":	", our customers are complaining that it’s very difficult to place orders through the new website."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Sally: "
            },
            {
              "text": "I think we "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"jumped the gun "
            },
            {
              "text":	"by not conducting focus groups with our customers before we launched our new website."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Larry: "
            },
            {
              "text": "More focus groups? "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"Every time I turn around"
            },
            {
              "text":	" we’re running focus groups! It’s "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"gotten out of hand"
            },
            {
              "text":	"."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Sally: "
            },
            {
              "markedText": "I beg to differ"
            },
            {
              "text":	". Focus groups are very important. They help us better understand our customer."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Julia: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Well, clearly you two "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"don’t see eye-to-eye"
            },
            {
              "text":	" on this issue."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Larry: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Ha! "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"That’s putting it lightly"
            },
            {
              "text":	"! Focus groups are a waste of time and..."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Julia: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Excuse me, let’s not "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"get off track"
            },
            {
              "text":	" here. Does anybody else want to "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"weigh in on the issue at hand"
            },
            {
              "text":	"?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Carl: "
            },
            {
              "text": "If I can "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"put in my two cents"
            },
            {
              "text":	", I agree with Sally that focus groups would’ve been a good idea."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Julia: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Well, enough about focus groups for now. Let’s move on to our next agenda item — planning for our "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"company offsite"
            },
            {
              "text":	"."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Larry: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Wait, I’m not finished talking about the website!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Julia: "
            },
            {
              "text": "We can "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"circle back to"
            },
            {
              "text":	" that at the end of our meeting if we have time. I want to keep us on schedule since I know many of us have another meeting at 11 o’clock."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
